flowchart TD
    A[Policy File] --> B[DocumentParser]
    B --> C[ParsedDocument]
    C --> D[TextChunker]
    D --> E[TextChunks]
    E --> F[EmbeddingEngine]
    F --> G[VectorStore: policy collection]

    H[ReferenceCatalog subcategories] --> I[HybridRetriever]
    G --> I
    I --> J[Stage A scoring/classification]
    J --> K{covered?}
    K -- yes --> L[covered_subcategories]
    K -- no --> M[Stage B constrained LLM reasoning]
    M --> N[GapDetail list]

    L --> O[GapAnalysisReport]
    N --> O
    O --> P[PolicyRevisionEngine]
    O --> Q[RoadmapGenerator]
    P --> R[revised_policy.md]
    Q --> S[implementation_roadmap.md/json]
    O --> T[gap_analysis_report.md/json]
    O --> U[AuditLogger entry]
